title: still haven't got my halloween minion icon?
body: Hi, so I waited patiently for my halloween icon/ beta icons and so far I got most of it even beta icon and TSM logo (which was given mistakenly).BUT I still haven't got my minion icon which was to summon Teemo(which I did more then once)

replies.body: I believe the Teemoing icons are done being sent out.  Hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) if you haven't received an icon yet.  We'll take a look at your case individually, and respond back asap!
